# Only files/ is consumed by the parent chart's .Files.Get calls.
# Everything below is source content for other pipelines (Docker image build,
# manual VPS deployment, CI config, repo metadata) and must not be packaged
# into the Helm chart artifact - some of these (gallery images) are large
# enough to blow past Helm's per-file size limit inside a chart archive.
images-build
vps-fallback
.github
.git
README.md
renovate.json
